🔤 Fonts Used

The fonts appear to be:

Primary Font

Segoe UI

This is the default Power BI font, commonly used for:

•	Titles

•	Axis labels

•	KPI cards

•	Slicers

•	Buttons

Font Hierarchy Used

Element	Font Style	Approx Size

Dashboard Title	Segoe UI Bold	32–40

Section Titles	Segoe UI Semibold	18–22

KPI Numbers	Segoe UI Bold	28–36

Chart Labels	Segoe UI Regular	12–14

Descriptions	Segoe UI Regular	11–13

